{"tid":1066584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"荃灣綫乘客轉月台往中上環 乘客：站與站之間停耐咗","createTime":"2019-03-18T03:45:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T04:35:09.000Z","uid":29627,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"897a3848f3c176f121bb92d75b3cf7539ba5812a","tid":1066584,"uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T03:45:35.000Z","msg":"荃灣綫乘客轉月台往中上環 乘客：站與站之間停耐咗 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190318/large/1552872936_336f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190318%2Flarge%2F1552872936_336f.jpg&h=6813f896&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n金鐘人流多，大學生孫小姐指有心理準備，沒有特別提早山門。<br />\n<br />\n荃灣綫來往中環至金鐘站暫停服務，由荃灣綫往中上環的乘客，到來金鐘站要落車，到下層港島綫2號月台繼續行程。<br />\n<br />\n大學生孫小姐由中環到大學站，她指好早知道有事故發生，但無提早出門口，「我本身有心理準備，都可以接受」，她說其實由金鐘到中環有其他選擇，「平時喺中環一程過，依家多咗喺金鐘轉車，不過時間上同平時差不多。」<br />\n<br />\n早上7時半左右人流未算太多，鄭先生指，中間的車站成日停，「多咗20分鐘，站與站之間停耐咗。」 <br />\n<br />\n李先生起床已知事故，因此早15分鐘出門口，但仍然比平日遲10分鐘左右。他希望政府對港鐵「監管好啲」。<br />\n<br />\n乘客張先生表示，是坐荃灣綫過海在金鐘站下車，早上知道事件後，便早10分鐘出門，列車沿途停站時間較平日多1、2分鐘，上班人潮和平日一樣。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190318/large/1552872825_8d30.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190318%2Flarge%2F1552872825_8d30.jpg&h=501a0bbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大學生孫小姐在金鐘轉車到大學站。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190318/59380620\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190318%2F59380620&d=0ENX7tHwQhT09cvOu3%2F4MyWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=b3578739\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190318%2F59380620&h=1582c34a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190318/59380620</a>"},{"pid":"c8b1f8535fed748d3d40664aba0bb92aac7e9e78","tid":1066584,"uid":160592,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T03:46:39.000Z","msg":"Gay test passed<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"363bd3b3ffc28f24dfe1b015565a6a82768c1c42","tid":1066584,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T03:47:54.000Z","msg":"Mandy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e65ddc4fcde6a3e10b17c56a3abee9e25c8e90f","tid":1066584,"uid":36004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T03:50:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e1f37347e790bb00e8678c97b0fb884add82d0f","tid":1066584,"uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T04:01:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef87fd6894b3b58fb5a763b3c6ba0b7ef5ebed10","tid":1066584,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T04:01:48.000Z","msg":"咁靚女都要搭地鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bc47a7edd63068348a850d1726cc833e201735c","tid":1066584,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T04:02:42.000Z","msg":"孫小姐做我女朋友我可以車你返學"},{"pid":"6d43b28a594bf78d68a8c90cb01efb3cae3c0eb2","tid":1066584,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T04:03:51.000Z","msg":"點解上邊張圖靚咁多"},{"pid":"f551d3ef96a86e928adc67c68b3e7f6b51f24a9f","tid":1066584,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T04:13:54.000Z","msg":"收唔收運輸兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p